<section class="calloutBox">
  <h2>What Most Gardeners Should Actually Use</h2>

  <p>
    For most balcony gardens, use a compact mini greenhouse shelf with a removable or roll-up cover and a stable frame. Position it in a protected spot and adjust airflow daily based on conditions.
  </p>

  <p>
    Avoid fully enclosed setups in warm sun, and prioritize stability and usability over maximum enclosure.
  </p>

  <p class="muted">
    Protect your plants, but don’t trap them.
  </p>
